Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.00,0:00:10.00,StaffTop,,0,0,0,,翻译：key 黑开水 夜夜  校对：小基友  时轴：琉璃色  后期：秋穗姬
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,======================================== TEXT ========================================
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.93,0:00:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,真可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.25,0:00:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,小小的日和
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.22,0:00:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,迷你和！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.61,0:00:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,迷你和？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.90,0:00:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,小时候你的头发是扎起来的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.77,0:00:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,那小春呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.61,0:00:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,这谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.58,0:00:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,是我是我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.70,0:00:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,小时候的我真是天使般可爱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.58,0:00:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,那份可爱如今跑到哪里去了…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.07,0:00:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,是恋小时候的照片 真可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.77,0:00:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,这个孩子是？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.89,0:00:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,是我弟弟 夏树
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.05,0:00:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,这孩子可淘气了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.08,0:00:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,好像是处于叛逆期来着？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.78,0:00:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,特别任性可烦人了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.29,0:00:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,不过 那会也挺可爱的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.89,0:00:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,在小春还小的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.64,0:00:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈和弟弟因车祸而去世了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.86,0:01:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我虽然在父亲病倒的时候被告知时日不多了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.77,0:01:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,但小春那时应该是突然就…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.03,0:01:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,家人突然去世时 她怀着什么样的心情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.98,0:01:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,毕竟是小春
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.86,0:01:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,肯定哭了许久吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.71,0:01:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,可是我…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.42,0:01:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,后面的照片呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.78,0:01:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.00,0:01:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然还有照片 但还没整理好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.64,0:01:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸和我都不是很擅长这方面的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.35,0:01:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.85,0:01:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,对了日和 这个是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.86,0:01:44.14,Default,,0,0,0,,边坐着船边钓鱼
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,=======OP======
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.17,0:03:18.96,Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)}『谢谢你』
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.05,0:03:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,这张是去钓鱼露营时候的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.51,0:03:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,经常和小恋她们一家一起去的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.36,0:03:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,钓鱼跟露营组合 还有这种操作
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.83,0:03:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.52,0:03:36.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我买蛋糕回来了 要吃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.36,0:03:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我要吃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.70,0:03:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,那我去泡茶了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.91,0:03:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢您
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.32,0:03:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,说起来 小春还对妈妈用敬语呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.97,0:03:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,有点意外
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.04,0:03:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然你说会有点隔阂 但还以为马上就能搞好关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.50,0:03:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,有点像跟个不熟的阿姨一起生活的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.06,0:04:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,日和不也是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.49,0:04:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,觉得家里像多了个不认识的叔叔那样的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.78,0:04:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,那个 确实
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.12,0:04:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,果然还是没办法一下子就亲近起来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.37,0:04:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,很久以前就这么想了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.69,0:04:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,小春这副口无遮拦的性格
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.91,0:04:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,好担心她的将来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.81,0:04:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,就这个了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.79,0:04:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.29,0:04:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,为了加深家人间的关系
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.77,0:04:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,就一起来钓鱼露营吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.71,0:04:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,不过 我们家有必要一起来的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.37,0:04:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,仔细这么一想的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.28,0:04:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么呀 不是说过会陪我钓鱼的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.03,0:04:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,就是啦恋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.54,0:04:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,别这么死板啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.01,0:04:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,这不应该是我们这边说的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.11,0:04:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,好啦好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.60,0:04:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,这么说来 现在山和的父母不在这里不是很奇怪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.32,0:05:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,只让隼人来照看小孩也太艰难了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.77,0:05:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,就拜托海凪夫妇帮忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.96,0:05:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,因为搭帐篷会减少钓鱼时间不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.91,0:05:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,是你干的好事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.80,0:05:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,疼疼疼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.00,0:05:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,好啦小恋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.28,0:05:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我们关系还比较尴尬啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.08,0:05:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,山和不在意的话倒没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.54,0:05:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,不过 一人至少也要钓到一条
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.95,0:05:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,没钓到的话今天就没有晚饭吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.55,0:05:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.17,0:05:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.79,0:05:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.83,0:05:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,恋 那边
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.17,0:05:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,快点！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.03,0:05:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,好好好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.43,0:05:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,好快
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.49,0:05:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,因为小恋经常帮她爸爸划船
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.66,0:05:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,所以划得特别好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.53,0:05:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,他们关系好好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.05,0:05:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,好 那我们也去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.87,0:05:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,小春就这么坐着
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.92,0:05:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.41,0:05:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.99,0:06:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,那么走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.29,0:06:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我想划划看
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.87,0:06:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,,可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.15,0:06:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,稍微有点沉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.67,0:06:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,,这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.19,0:06:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,等下 小春
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.36,0:06:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,要回岸边了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.98,0:06:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.40,0:06:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,她们在玩什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.47,0:07:01.89,Default,,0,0,0,,好帅
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.51,0:07:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,那个 小春小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.20,0:07:09.53,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fn方正少儿_GBK\fs40\bord3\3c&FFFFFF&\fsp10\c&H4B76FB&\pos(612.12,883.394)}憧憬的目光
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.05,0:07:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.78,0:07:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害 好漂亮的抛竿
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.08,0:07:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,还有为什么突然抛向不同的方向？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.52,0:07:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,因为看到鱼影了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.44,0:07:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我光看着日和钓鱼的样子就已经很享受了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.71,0:07:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,自己钓的话会更有趣哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.22,0:07:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,帐篷搭好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.70,0:07:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.66,0:07:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,那么开始做午饭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.46,0:07:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.20,0:07:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.73,0:07:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,他们两个说在船上吃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.91,0:07:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,好赖皮
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.23,0:07:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我们也想在船上吃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.11,0:07:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,不可以任性
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.88,0:07:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.83,0:08:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,因为是在船上 所以就准备了方便手抓着吃的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.25,0:08:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.20,0:08:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.28,0:08:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,在大自然之中
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.32,0:08:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,坐在船上吃便当 多是一件美事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.53,0:08:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,到了秋天还能看到漫山红叶 特别漂亮的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.26,0:08:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.17,0:08:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,那到秋天再来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.45,0:08:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,到时候再问问妈妈他们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.05,0:08:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.52,0:08:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,最近感觉钓鱼好有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.69,0:08:48.07,Default,,0,0,0,,大概是因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.08,0:08:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,不愧是我 做得真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.59,0:08:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,肯定是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.62,0:08:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,是梅干
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.80,0:08:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,难道你不喜欢吃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.49,0:08:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,不是呀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.38,0:09:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,就想到还是第一次在钓鱼的时候吃到梅干 就
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.84,0:09:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你想 梅干不是有防腐的效果吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.05,0:09:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,不容易「食物中毒」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.76,0:09:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,所以会让钓鱼也不容易「中」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.94,0:09:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,如果带了梅干来钓鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.24,0:09:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,就会空手而归 有这么一个说法
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.68,0:09:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,还有 掌管渔业的神明惠比寿
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.19,0:09:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,也不喜欢吃酸的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.41,0:09:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,所以说它不太吉利…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.20,0:09:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.20,0:09:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,要是因为这个饭团完全钓不上来的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.95,0:09:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,,这只是迷信啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.55,0:09:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,这不都已经钓上来两条了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.52,0:09:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,其他的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.36,0:09:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,,其他的菜没关系吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.10,0:09:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系 没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.31,0:09:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.07,0:09:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,作为饭后甜点
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.86,0:09:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我还烤了些香蕉挞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.76,0:09:49.47,Default,,0,0,0,,香蕉也有什么说法吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.94,0:10:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,完全钓不到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.01,0:10:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然我本来就钓不到
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.69,0:10:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,,时段已经结束了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.86,0:10:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,时段？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.37,0:10:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,指鱼吃饭的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.91,0:10:14.85,Default,,0,0,0,,在这段时间里比较容易钓到鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.36,0:10:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,所以不是梅干的错
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.62,0:10:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,咦 下雨了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.89,0:10:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,好像是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.42,0:10:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,开始下了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.80,0:10:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,小春 赶紧穿上雨衣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.73,0:10:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我们回得去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.28,0:10:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,,山里的天气很不稳定
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.39,0:10:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得这雨很快就会停了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.85,0:10:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,日和 快看快看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.42,0:10:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,这里有好多鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.91,0:10:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,真的诶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.00,0:10:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,是鲤鱼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.03,0:10:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,小鲤鱼 居然待在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.07,0:10:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,鱼也在避雨吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.50,0:10:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,明明在水里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.75,0:11:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,这个湖跟以往相比没什么变化
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.40,0:11:08.89,Default,,0,0,0,,但我还是第一次看到雨中的风景
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.36,0:11:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,日和？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.15,0:11:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,感觉还挺有趣的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.02,0:11:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,这里就像个秘密基地 真开心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.08,0:11:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.38,0:11:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,最近
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.44,0:11:33.89,Default,,0,0,0,,感觉钓鱼好有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.16,0:11:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,大概是因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.47,0:11:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,肯定是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.66,0:11:42.47,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.78,0:11:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然想这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.35,0:11:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,但是太羞耻了 还是别说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.80,0:11:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了 雨停了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.20,0:11:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,但没准马上又开始下雨了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.56,0:12:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,时间也差不多了 该回去了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.23,0:12:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我一条都没钓到…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.19,0:12:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,日和
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.21,0:12:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,鱼靠到好近的地方来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.97,0:12:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,那条鱼 好像在吃小虫子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.10,0:12:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,用小虫饵吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.40,0:12:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,小虫？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.49,0:12:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,就是特别小的毛钩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.02,0:12:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,给我下小恋的毛钩盒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.88,0:12:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.71,0:12:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我来换毛钩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.74,0:12:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,小春开始准备抛线吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.63,0:12:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.95,0:12:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,日和打算让我来钓
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.56,0:12:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,压力好大
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.96,0:12:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,来 抛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.41,0:12:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,心乱了线也乱了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.77,0:12:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系 把鱼竿放下来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.32,0:13:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,上钩了！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.75,0:13:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,保持冷静
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.86,0:13:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,不要让线过于松下来 往自己这边拉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.22,0:13:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,靠近之后 我就用网捞起来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.28,0:13:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.28,0:13:45.07,Default,,0,0,0,,钓上来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.25,0:13:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,你是哪位
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.92,0:13:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,鳟鱼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.44,0:13:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,大哥我错了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.95,0:13:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,在设施入口附近
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.93,0:13:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,有一家店能帮你烧烤钓上来的鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.82,0:13:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,要让他帮忙烤小春钓上来的鱼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.51,0:14:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.38,0:14:14.01,Default,,0,0,0,,用人类作比喻就是火刑
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.32,0:14:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么要用人类…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.75,0:14:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直很向往这种漫画里的吃法！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.96,0:14:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我能开动了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.00,0:14:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,吃吧吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.47,0:14:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.37,0:14:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,第一次自己钓上来鱼的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.06,0:14:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,不是 你倒是说点啥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.39,0:15:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,跟不认识的阿姨住在一起嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.40,0:15:02.27,Default,,0,0,0,,不也挺好的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.41,0:15:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,对父母说敬语什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.68,0:15:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,搞得跟大户人家一样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.07,0:15:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,哎呀 真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.41,0:15:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.47,0:15:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,小春 切开鱼肚子之后把内脏拿出来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.46,0:15:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.81,0:15:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,对对对
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.41,0:15:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,就算是亲生的 关系不好的亲子也大有人在
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.29,0:15:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,还有一点都不关心孩子的家长
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.82,0:15:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你们不会是觉得我家父女关系很好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.55,0:15:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.11,0:15:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,隔壁家的草坪更绿 说的就是这种情况吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.77,0:15:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,其他家庭的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.79,0:15:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,你总归只能知道表面情况
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.29,0:15:38.59,Default,,0,0,0,,只看到幸福的一面
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.87,0:15:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,然后想着自己也要这样才行 可不能这么想
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.06,0:15:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.49,0:15:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,就没有什么「该做的事情」是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.93,0:15:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,跟你们说句实话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.42,0:15:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直到了最近 才开始把父母当个人来看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.01,0:15:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,什么 哲学？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.89,0:16:00.47,Default,,0,0,0,,在这之前就只是当成父母
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.01,0:16:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,在为人父母之前 首先是个人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.94,0:16:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,也会不断地烦恼 不断地失败
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.09,0:16:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,即使成为了大人了 也会犯很多的错
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.20,0:16:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,自从发现这一点后 我心里就轻松了些
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.17,0:16:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,烤得不错
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.50,0:16:23.81,Default,,0,0,0,,小春厨房！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.97,0:16:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,首先  准备好加盐烤过的虹鳟
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.12,0:16:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,就是为此烤的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.38,0:16:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,今天因为有小朋友在场
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.41,0:16:34.57,Default,,0,0,0,,就用水来代替白葡萄酒倒入锅内
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.34,0:16:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,原来用水也可以呀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.03,0:16:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,之后放入虹鳟
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.93,0:16:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,再加入蛤蜊和小番茄  盖上锅盖
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.82,0:16:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,然后稍微煮一会儿
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.31,0:16:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,虹鳟作主材料的意式海鲜乱炖出锅
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.74,0:16:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,一如既往的厉害呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.97,0:16:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我也好想像小春这样会做饭
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.92,0:17:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈用微波炉都会爆炸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.46,0:17:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,那只是冒烟而已啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.29,0:17:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,迄今为止你们是怎么解决吃饭问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.99,0:17:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,以前是爸爸负责做饭的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.21,0:17:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,自从他住院之后
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.51,0:17:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,更多的是吃超市的熟食 或者在外面吃了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.50,0:17:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,要忙工作什么杂七杂八的  有点腾不出时间
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.46,0:17:22.49,Default,,0,0,0,,不像样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.79,0:17:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,完全没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.37,0:17:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.29,0:17:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,超市的熟食很棒的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.54,0:17:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我也经常买的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.80,0:17:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.67,0:17:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.73,0:17:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,对了对了  我在附近找到一家好吃的熟食店
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.47,0:17:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,在哪呀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.55,0:17:40.04,DefaultTop,,0,0,0,,很近的很近的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.71,0:17:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,好狡猾 下一个到我啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.86,0:17:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,再来一次  再来一次
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.11,0:17:47.09,Default,,0,0,0,,好好好  这次好了就轮到虎君了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.09,0:17:49.64,Default,,0,0,0,,绝对的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.76,0:17:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你们两个 都找到了玩伴呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.71,0:17:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我开动啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.38,0:18:10.41,Default,,0,0,0,,鱼热腾腾的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.46,0:18:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,很香 很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.00,0:18:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,吃自己钓的鱼做下酒菜下酒真是一绝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.72,0:18:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,出现了 大叔笑话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.57,0:18:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,虹君 好吃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.32,0:18:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思  连小虹吃饭都得麻烦您照顾
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.05,0:18:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.46,0:18:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,可是 难得的饭菜都要冷了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.40,0:18:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.82,0:18:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,好吃吗虹君
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.57,0:18:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,日和
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.59,0:18:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,这个 请用
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.81,0:18:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.13,0:19:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,日和
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.69,0:19:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我先去哄小不点们睡觉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.28,0:19:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我们也去刷个牙睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.66,0:19:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.50,0:19:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,远离火堆之后就冷起来了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.63,0:19:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,睡袋放了暖宝宝 再努力一下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.92,0:19:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.21,0:19:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,小春 看天上
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.41,0:19:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,好漂亮  名副其实的满天星
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.05,0:19:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,那个难不成就是北斗七星
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.08,0:19:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,真的诶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.77,0:20:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,总感觉和教科书上的不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.22,0:20:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,什么意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.60,0:20:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,,你看嘛  星星不止七个
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.60,0:20:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,因为城里看不到小的星星嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.61,0:20:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,是这样呀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.61,0:20:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,即使看不见 但确实就在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.33,0:20:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,即使看不见 但确实…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.20,0:20:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,父亲认得出我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.86,0:20:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,是说我的父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.02,0:20:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,父亲去世之后我长高了很多
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.42,0:20:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,所以觉得看到现在的我 可能会认不出了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.39,0:20:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,认得出的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.15,0:20:46.99,Default,,0,0,0,,日和 今天是真开心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.60,0:20:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.58,0:20:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,所以放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.23,0:20:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,日和的爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.97,0:20:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,还有我的妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.17,0:21:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,肯定都会认得我们的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.36,0:21:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,只要笑容和从前一样 不曾改变
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.41,0:21:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.26,0:21:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.30,0:21:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.03,0:21:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,小恋
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.21,0:21:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,在露营地 晚上要保持安静
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.01,0:21:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.72,0:21:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我们下次再一起来钓鱼露营吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.73,0:21:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,就说到了下次了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.12,0:22:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,下次就在枫叶变红的季节
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.34,0:22:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,观赏枫叶的钓鱼露营哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.19,0:22:10.95,Default,,0,0,0,,标题是不是太长了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.11,0:22:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,确实
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,=========ED========
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.26,0:23:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么去钓鱼不能带着香蕉哇
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.10,0:23:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,在还没有发明出冰箱的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.14,0:23:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,装上船的香蕉长虫子了 似乎是因为这个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.99,0:23:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,就是图个好口彩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.85,0:23:59.53,Default,,0,0,0,,这怎么会banana
